Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 不要回头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:14.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 迈步出发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪是闪闪发光的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.80,0:00:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一步 都化为甘霖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.78,0:00:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更加自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要的东西就舍去 这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在无限广阔的心中蔓延开来哟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于受伤时刻之外　看不见的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:54.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若现在开始映入双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just Try-again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.01,0:01:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得强大 抓住机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 无论何时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight 都要坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.04,0:01:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦想绝对能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.13,0:01:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多遥远 都不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.13,0:01:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fight Fight 更能感觉到明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫战部渡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了打倒支配了在遥远天空上的星界山的多坏达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以第七星界为目标展开了冒险旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.14,0:01:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入了暗黑空间的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解开了光龙剑的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.81,0:01:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙神丸也增强了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.52,0:01:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复活变成了龙星丸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.98,0:01:54.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着是第五星界了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.01,0:01:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也会是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二十九话\N在西部之镇很想睡!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.11,0:02:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…到底干了什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.01,0:02:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡他们不是终于也上到第五星界了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:31.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的残局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.99,0:02:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们打算怎样收拾?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要等黑龙角一修理好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.08,0:02:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今次一定会把渡…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事只是说有用吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不,多支达路将军
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第五星界的波士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟也绽奥里零是我的部下…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,你要替我收拾渡吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.61,0:03:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今次便交给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好好的给我看,雪京芭!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太有个性了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:39.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是雪京芭大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟也绽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个渡终于来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:46.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有松卸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入了由我支配的这个星界是他的末日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔…你干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:03:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为能瞒得过我双眼吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不是太可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.21,0:04:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好拜托你了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后不有型吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜柑小山羊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟也绽,型男混蛋大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是没变不知你到底是有礼貌还是粗鲁的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:24.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪京芭大人刚刚下了命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那个渡的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我出马的话渡只是小儿科
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么便拜托你了(说话方式被污染了)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次到下一个星界都要坐这个的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下身体支持不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师还是没变是超重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:05:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,我要在此离开一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛要走吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我上次说的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一个我非找不可的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸟先生,一起上路吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还可以随时见面的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古拿玛,你一切要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子,对不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里便是第五星界吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是沙漠世界吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边有市镇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,去看看吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的,过彩虹桥时已令我相当疲倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一个没精神的市镇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先去找休息的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,那间好像是旅馆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.57,0:06:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请放入住宿费
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住宿费是多少钱?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么贵吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不可以少些?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:07:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没钱的家伙不可以休息!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以休息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我人生中最不幸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到其他的地方找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已想睡得不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你说不行了也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤脑筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,请问你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有比这旅馆更便宜的旅馆?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅馆只有这一间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说这里只有一间旅馆吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对,只有一间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么连我也想睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:07:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了?师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股不知被什么刺了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.32,0:08:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人?快出来!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等我!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔针,拔针!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这便完了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:28.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个市镇到底怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以睡的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.55,0:08:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫尊尼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.48,0:08:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么尊尼,不可以睡是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是支配这个刺刺镇的蜜柑小山羊的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜柑小山羊在这个镇定下了一条绝不能睡的法律呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是不可能的法律呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以睡的便只有刚才那间刺刺旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:09:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是住宿费这么贵的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也不能入住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是如果在其他地方睡的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便会好像刚才一样从仙人掌中飞出针来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这是为了什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为黑暗从东面开始来吞噬这个星界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:17.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么刚才的便是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那黑暗里面是可怕的魔界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.48,0:09:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论哪个镇的居民都开始逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以蜜柑小山羊便弄疲累镇上的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.98,0:09:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令我们不能逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能饶恕!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的坏蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剑部武一郎绝对不会饶恕!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很想睡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已不行了…站不起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以啊,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是就算你这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面的眼皮和下面的眼皮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也奇怪的很想紧贴在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:09:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊,对了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡他们在闭上了的眼皮上用笔画上了眼珠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么,什么?怎么了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着了的家伙在哪里!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了,是蜜柑小山羊啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙便是蜜柑小山羊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问你这混蛋是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救世主渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜柑小山羊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.74,0:11:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了后,便不能再任由你横行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋便是渡大人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.34,0:11:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯了法还这么大口气?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以睡的法律!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.55,0:11:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没可能会守的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,那么决斗吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.98,0:11:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓?等…等等啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:29.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这没胆鬼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斗也好,什么也好,我都接受!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜柑小山羊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次决斗 输的一方便要离开这个镇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有逃还敢来我要称赞你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过反正也是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:11:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真卑鄙!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有说过不准出术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…哪一位?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这和我什么关系也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.74,0:12:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不太喜欢以多欺少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么穿成这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是决斗时的正常服式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正蠢材 上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些不是水枪吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊,被真枪打中的话会很痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会痛的?你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也快用这个攻击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被水击中的话便输了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,这样的话什么也好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:13:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这算是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是表示已被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:07.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是太明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了,没水了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子,之后拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…那算什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要得意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.05,0:13:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好 海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜柑小山羊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快照约定离开这市镇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦,啰嗦!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:49.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你看我会怎样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子,谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是为了你而干的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:13:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是你这么悠闲可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅,起来啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子,刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想想法子对付后面那家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知什么事,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍法,用萝卜引马跑之术!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么令人觉得很怀念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,马先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得好,火美子!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帐,把这个献给你!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃得掉吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸,一口气解决他!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超飞龙拳!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白银光绿攻击!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次由这边上了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞起来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有本事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧,龙星丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不能让你成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹波糖飞弹!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸,快避开那些飞弹!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.74,0:16:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行,不管飞到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些飞弹也能射来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,升上去吧,龙星丸!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你去到哪里也不能逃离这些飞弹的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.86,0:17:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话,只有用超天空幻龙波了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超天空幻龙波?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你也许会是太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸,我要试试!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超天空幻龙波!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,再多忍耐一会!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.32,0:17:54.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终…终于停了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道什么事但好像是机会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我用这个来替你了结吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡那家伙,要给我多少次麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要阻碍我,你这家伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有时间和你玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我清醒一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:18:57.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,振作点!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:19:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我便没有欠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海火子,你来救我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手来了,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.73,0:19:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气收拾你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙星丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再试多一次超天空幻龙波吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是渡,如果像刚才那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题,今次会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:24.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好,我相信渡的力量!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超天空幻龙波!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡,不要再勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样…就这样子升上去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会输的!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得很好,渡!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.13,0:20:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我晕了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光龙剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必杀!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光龙剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.86,0:20:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被干掉了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.70,0:20:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武一郎先生,火美子妹妹,很多谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样大家便可以放心睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不,真没面目见你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在渡战斗的期间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下好像一直在睡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来…渡先生呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看,他一个人战斗令他十分疲倦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是各位之后要去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之打算往那黑暗中去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许敌人的大将会在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么请大家保重了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.61,0:21:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡完全没有醒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中间也要好好休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.25,0:21:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他是唯一的救世主呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要,我要和渡玩!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,火美子,不要这么任性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.23,0:21:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要和渡玩,便要玩!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.73,0:21:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.75,0:21:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不理你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.99,0:21:58.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来玩,来玩!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.97,0:21:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 火美子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去了哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.07,0:22:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂,火美子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.70,0:22:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火美子,你在哪里啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.04,0:22:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 阴霾的天空里乌云渐渐散去 阳光透过云层照了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.61,0:22:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人仰望这天空的哪个角落
